DISCLAIMER

This software is designed to assist school counselors in guiding students through
the college admissions process. The recommendations and analyses provided by this
software are for informational and guidance purposes only and should not be
considered as professional advice or guarantees of admission outcomes.

Users should:
- Verify all university data and admission statistics independently
- Consult with qualified educational counselors and admission professionals
- Review official university websites for current requirements and deadlines
- Comply with all applicable laws and regulations regarding student data privacy (FERPA)
- Use AI-generated content as a starting point, not as final or authoritative advice

The developers and contributors of this software:
- Make no warranties regarding the accuracy or completeness of the information
- Are not responsible for admission decisions or outcomes
- Do not guarantee acceptance to any educational institution
- Are not liable for any damages arising from the use of this software

PRIVACY NOTE

This software processes student data locally and via third-party APIs (OpenAI).
Users are responsible for:
- Obtaining necessary permissions to collect and process student data
- Complying with FERPA, COPPA, and other relevant privacy regulations
- Securing API keys and preventing unauthorized access
- Protecting student privacy and confidentiality

